Foldback / Wavefold
  - Captain Beefheart — "Frownland" (not literally a wavefolder, but the vibe)                            
  - Depeche Mode — "Personal Jesus" (Buchla-style synth tones use wavefolding extensively)                
  - Trent Reznor / Nine Inch Nails — "Wish" (the metallic, buzzing synth timbres owe a lot to wavefolding)
  - Suzanne Ciani's early Buchla recordings are pure wavefolder tone — the Buchla 259 Complex Waveform    
  Generator is a wavefolder at its core                                                                   
  - Make Noise and Intellijel modular stuff you hear in current electronic music (Alessandro Cortini's    
  solo work)
